#. Tag: title
#: other_features.docbook:2
#, no-c-format
msgid "Other Features"
msgstr "Outras funcionalidades"

#. Tag: title
#: other_features.docbook:4
#, no-c-format
msgid "Other &umbrello; Features"
msgstr "Outras funcionalidades de &umbrello;"

#. Tag: para
#: other_features.docbook:5
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This chapter will briefly explain some other features &umbrello; offers you."
msgstr ""
"Este capítulo describe por riba algunhas funcionalidades adicionais que "
"ofrece &umbrello;."

#. Tag: title
#: other_features.docbook:7
#, no-c-format
msgid "Copying objects as PNG images"
msgstr "Copiar obxectos como imaxes PNG"

#. Tag: para
#: other_features.docbook:8
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Apart from offering you the normal copy, cut and paste functionality that "
#| "you would expect to copy objects between different diagrams, &umbrello; "
#| "can copy the objects as PNG pictures so that you can insert them into any "
#| "other type of document. You do not need to do anything special to use "
#| "this feature, just select an object from a diagram (Class, Actor, &etc;) "
#| "and copy it (<keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>C</keycap></keycombo>, or using the "
#| "menu), then open a &kword; document (or any program into which you can "
#| "paste images) and select <guimenuitem>Paste</guimenuitem>. This is a "
#| "great feature to export parts of your diagram as simple pictures."
msgid ""
"Apart from offering you the normal copy, cut and paste functionality that "
"you would expect to copy objects between different diagrams, &umbrello; can "
"copy the objects as PNG pictures so that you can insert them into any other "
"type of document. You do not need to do anything special to use this "
"feature, just select an object from a diagram (Class, Actor, &etc;) and copy "
"it (<keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>C</keycap></keycombo>, or using the menu), then "
"open a <application>Calligra Words</application> document (or any program "
"into which you can paste images) and select <guimenuitem>Paste</"
"guimenuitem>. This is a great feature to export parts of your diagram as "
"simple pictures."
msgstr ""
"Ademais das funcións normais de copiar, cortar e apegar que serven para "
"copiar obxectos entre distintos diagramas, &umbrello; pode copiar os "
"obxectos como imaxes PNG para que os poida inserir en outros tipos de "
"documento. Non precisa facer nada especial para usar esta funcionalidade, só "
"escolla un obxecto no diagrama (Clase, Actor, &etc;) e cópieo "
"(<keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>C</keycap></keycombo>, ou mediante o menú), logo "
"abra un documento de &kword; (ou de calquer programa onde poida apegar "
"imaxes) e escolla <guimenuitem>Apegar</guimenuitem>. Esta é unha "
"funcionalidade perfeita para exportar partes do diagrama como imaxes simples."

#. Tag: title
#: other_features.docbook:18
#, no-c-format
msgid "Exporting to an Image"
msgstr "Exportar para unha imaxe"

#. Tag: para
#: other_features.docbook:19
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can also export a complete diagram as an image. The only thing you need "
"to do is select the diagram you want to export, and then the option "
"<guimenuitem>Export as Picture...</guimenuitem> from the <guimenu>Diagram</"
"guimenu> menu."
msgstr ""
"Tamén pode exportar un diagrama enteiro como unha imaxe. A única cousa que "
"precisa facer é escoller o diagrama que quere exportar, e logo a opción "
"<guimenuitem>Exportar como imaxe…</guimenuitem> no menú <guimenu>Diagrama</"
"guimenu>."

#. Tag: para
#: other_features.docbook:24
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can export multiple diagrams at once using the <guimenuitem>Export "
"Diagrams as Pictures...</guimenuitem> option from the <guimenu>File</"
"guimenu> menu. With this, you can also set the image resolution, so that the "
"images won't be as blurry."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: title
#: other_features.docbook:31
#, no-c-format
msgid "Printing"
msgstr "Imprimir"

#. Tag: para
#: other_features.docbook:32
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&umbrello; allows you to print individual diagrams. Press the "
"<guiicon>Print</guiicon> button on the application toolbar or selecting the "
"<guimenuitem>Print</guimenuitem> option from the <guimenu>File</guimenu> "
"menu will give you a standard &kde; Print dialog from where you can print "
"your diagrams."
msgstr ""
"&umbrello; permítelle imprimir diagramas individualmente. Prema o botón "
"<guiicon>Imprimir</guiicon> na barra de ferramentas do aplicativo ou escolla "
"a opción <guimenuitem>Imprimir</guimenuitem> no menú <guimenu>Ficheiro</"
"guimenu> e amosarase o diálogo estándar de &kde; para imprimir."

#. Tag: title
#: other_features.docbook:40
#, no-c-format
msgid "Logical Folders"
msgstr "Cartafoles lóxicos"

#. Tag: para
#: other_features.docbook:41
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To better organize your model, especially for larger projects, you can "
"create logical folders in the Tree View. Just select the option "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>New</guimenu><guimenuitem>Folder</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> from the context menu of the default folders in the Tree View to "
"create them. Folders can be nested, and you can move objects around by "
"dragging them from one folder and dropping them into another."
msgstr ""
"Para organizar mellor o modelo, en especial en proxectos grandes, pode crear "
"cartafoles lóxicos na Vista en Árbore. Simplesmente escolla a opción "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Novo</guimenu><guimenuitem>Cartafol</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> no menú contextual dos cartafoles predeterminados na vista en "
"árbore para crealos. Os cartafoles poden estar uns dentro dos outros, e pode "
"mover obxectos entre eles arrastrándoo dun para o outro."

#. Tag: screeninfo
